m
http://aws.typepad.com/aws/2012/12/aws-sdk-for-nodejs-now-available-in-pre=
view-form.html

  This SDK, direct from Amazon, allows you to access Amazon Web Services (=
S3,
  Elastic Compute Cloud, DynamoDB, etc.) from Node.

Notes on the TC39 Meetings in November 2012
https://github.com/rwldrn/tc39-notes/tree/master/es6/2012-11

  TC39 (=E2=80=9CTechnical Committee 39=E2=80=9D) is working on the ECMASc=
ript 6 standard.
